definition: perfect/excellent/brought to the utmost degree
to (a place)/until (a time)/up to/to go/to arrive/(verb complement denoting completion or result of an action)

home/family/(polite) my (sister, uncle etc)/classifier for families or businesses/refers to the philosophical schools of pre-Han China/noun suffix for a specialist in some activity, such as a musician or revolutionary, corresponding to English -ist, -er, -ary or -ian/CL:個|个[ge4]

sentences.english: Put the clothes into the dryer when you get home.
sentences.chinese: 到家后就把衣服放进干衣机里。

sentences.english: If Fred didn't leave till five o'clock, he can't be home yet.
sentences.chinese: 如果弗雷德五点钟以后走护短，现在还不可能到家。

sentences.english: I don't know how long I'll have to play and practice before I can gain that kind of skills.
sentences.chinese: 这样的绝活不知道要练多久才能到家和随心应手？

sentences.english: The tired children don't get home until 7:00.
sentences.chinese: 疲惫不堪的孩子们要道晚上7点才能到家。
我们周日早上一点半到家。

sentences.english: They were not welcomed home very  cordially by their mother.
sentences.chinese: 到家以后，母亲并不怎么热诚地欢迎她们。

sentences.english: I was supposed to be at home for dinner at six and it's already seven-thirty.
sentences.chinese: 我应该六点到家吃晚饭的，可现在已经是七点半了。

sentences.english: They thought the wonton soup and milky coffee combination was hilarious.
sentences.chinese: 宝钗和黛玉觉得馄饨汤和奶咖啡的搭配滑稽到家了。

sentences.english: I often walk the 3 mi. home from work rather than take the subway.
sentences.chinese: 从公司到家，有三公里，我都是步行回往，不坐地铁。

sentences.english: I will be home after across this tunnel.
sentences.chinese: 过了这个小洞子，就马上到家了。

sentences.english: Before Willem got home, the phone rang.
sentences.chinese: 威廉还没有到家，电话就响了。

sentences.english: I have the highest opinion in the world of Edward's heart.
sentences.chinese: 我对爱德华的那颗心算是佩服到家了。

sentences.english: But he also knew where she'd be likely to go on the way home from the mall.
sentences.chinese: 但是，他又想，在从购物中心到家的路上也很有可能。

sentences.english: Chain to implement unified prices, the establishment of customer files at home.
sentences.chinese: 实行连锁经营，统一售价，建立顾客档案服务到家。

sentences.english: The westerner thought that leaves behind the address to the human, must ask opposite party to sojourn proficiently .
sentences.chinese: 西方人认为给人留下住址，就得请对方到家作客。

sentences.english: It's home, so that's where I'll be.
sentences.chinese: 到家了，这正是我想落叶归根之处。
